Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.49,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,運転できるの　善次郎さん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,運転できるのかって
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.19,0:19:45.91,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,むろん
