Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.11,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんでなんで
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.37,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちょっともう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.17,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,もう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああ　もう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.39,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんだこれ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.52,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子で戻れるんじゃないの　違うの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,って　ちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.56,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,くれぐれも気をつけるんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.77,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ありがとう　お母さん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,行ってきます
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,もし生きてる貂熊がいたら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.28,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,バカなことやってないで　とっとと帰ってこいって伝えてね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.20,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.08,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必ずお父さんに伝える
