Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.69,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇 这个是什么知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.78,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎 那边很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里面有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:47.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.56,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吧吧的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,庞太郎那个臭小子真他妈走狗屎运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,说了多少次要他放弃7G
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,这种计划是不可能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:57.82,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:02.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,它能够破坏物理定律 但他却无视研究人员警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.28,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,只盲目接受「牟利者」提供的不可靠信息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,在最坏的情况下没有放弃 反而招来了最不愿发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,草泥马的婊子跟谁过不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,为了不让我打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,用软绵绵手术让我变得软绵绵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,完全无法控制 简直凶残到毫无人性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,所以你给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.50,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我绝对要把7G停给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.87,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不会让你霸占池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等会 你说池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.16,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.89,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我不能就这样离开池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我要马上去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:30.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,迫不得已 我善治郎这局身躯将搭乘这两千序列
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不对 等会 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你是 千仓静留对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你小的时候跌到泥沟里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎样都行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,重要的是你是如何把两千系列开过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.49,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你会开火车吗 善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你说我会不会开火车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:45.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,咋了咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,给我再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再来一次
