Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.52,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子不是能把他变回去吗 不对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂 你
