Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,无论如何 都要确保自身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,谢谢你 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我出发了
